The secretary of the interior.

849
00:55:12.809 --> 00:55:14.686
Manuel Bartlett…

850
00:55:14.769 --> 00:55:17.272
Tell him the Union of Journalists is here.

851
00:55:19.190 --> 00:55:21.318
The secretary of the interior.

852
