854
00:55:26.740 --> 00:55:31.494
Two seconds later. by some miracle.

855
00:55:31.578 --> 00:55:34.247
Manuel Bartlett appeared and met with us.

856
00:55:35.206 --> 00:55:40.378
We told him we were angry

857
00:55:40.462 --> 00:55:42.964
