946
01:01:29.477 --> 01:01:34.065
Then Zorrilla showed up
at my office and said.

947
01:01:34.148 --> 01:01:37.944
"I've come to say farewell."

948
01:01:38.027 --> 01:01:39.779
"Where are you going?"

949
01:01:40.279 --> 01:01:45.118
"The secretary has appointed me
